


DATABASE OBJECTS

Actium::DB
  -- generic database role, contains dbh, lists of tables

Actium::DB::FileMaker_ODBC
  -- class composing Actium::DB for FileMaker databases

Actium::DB::SQLite
  -- class composing Actium::DB for SQLite databases

Actium::DB::ActiumDB
  -- subclass of Actium::DB with methods that require multiple 
     Actium tables

Actium::DB::Xhea
  -- subclass of Actium::DB with methods that require multiple 
     Xhea tables. 

Actium::DB::GTFS
  -- subclass of Actium::DB with methods that require multiple 
     GTFS tables

Actium::DB::Table - generic table
   includes routines like read_from_csv, read_from_xhea_xml,  etc
   also things like all_in_columns_key

Actium::DB::ActiumDB::Signs, Actium::DB::Xhea::Stops, etc. - 
   specific tables, subclasses of DB::Table with methods specific to each
   table



